{"tid":223121,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返沒自信的毒男一篇文","createTime":"2017-04-30T05:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T06:34:25.000Z","uid":12458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ee0b40ef5a77b95301d6d5542d7ecc902d44a1","tid":223121,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"係講飲茶 話有架車果篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想睇返 有無backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d052c06143193e641a2d60de3f306537766a912c","tid":223121,"uid":27777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"google啦問"},{"pid":"402c5490cc7f46ef5c1d0feb7308484d6f6b5e8c","tid":223121,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>google啦問</blockquote><br />\n搵過無呀"},{"pid":"9e5f18c97d76a9b07f1a9ffe48e4e8cd3723b621","tid":223121,"uid":75792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"呢篇?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同女友都一齊左2年 但舊年因為公司人手唔夠 同埋我個職位比較上重要 所以我冇假放 亦懶得去女友屋企拜年<br />\n<br />\n因為自己又窮 冇用 冇自信 矮毒Seven宅樣樣齊 我都唔明點解女朋友會揀我 仲一齊到2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但今年個經理話比我休息下 唔洗番 難得唔洗麥麥送我緊係即刻同女友講話可以去佢屋企啦 <br />\n<br />\n佢以為我今年都冇假放仲嬲向左走向右走左我一排 話我唔敢面對佢屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n年初4夜晚我就去向左走向右走左女友屋企 一入屋發現唔單只家人 原來佢D親戚都係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我太驚唔知講咩好 除左女友啊哥我其他人都未見過 我SAY左聲HI之後就拿拿林痴埋去佢啊哥到傾計 但其實佢啊哥都唔多LIKE我 成日覺得我冇上進心冇目標好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為佢啊哥之前同我小中學都同一間 但後來我中4轉左校冇再見過 就係第2間學校果陣識左而家女友 <br />\n<br />\n過左半粒鐘 伯母就話樓下酒樓訂左位 一齊去食飯 大約都有成13人左右 <br />\n<br />\n行緊去果陣我心諗: 一陣我唔向左走向右走出聲潛哂水等佢地唔記得我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我真係好驚比佢地問問題 <br />\n<br />\n點知一坐落冇耐 女友個姑姐就望住我 上下打量一番之後問:咦 啊X個男朋友啊? 幾大啊 而家讀緊咩啊? <br />\n<br />\n我:21<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都算係讀緊港大課程啦.. <br />\n<br />\n佢:嘩 咁叻仔架 讀咩科架 <br />\n<br />\n我:都係讀果D野啦..BUSINESS咁啦..哈哈.. <br />\n<br />\n喱個時候女友啊哥就插咀話:咩BUSINESS啊 乜你係大學學位黎架咩 <br />\n<br />\n我心諗:Hi Auntie就算唔係都唔好出聲啦Hi Hi仔 之後細細聲講左句:none of your business啊Auntie... <br />\n<br />\n點知條Hi Hi聽到之後仲火上加油話:佢係向左走向右走讀緊港大 SPACE仔炸 細個果陣你志願係太空人喎 而家咪夢想成真囉 <br />\n<br />\n好彩女友即刻幫我解圍話:唔係架 佢好大機會入得番大學架 而家仲半工讀 好勤力架 岩岩先公司趕番番黎 所以先遲左黎炸 <br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後就食住個勢話:係囉 同埋喱頭地方細 比較難搵車位啊 遲左少少要大家等唔好意思 <br />\n<br />\n伯母一聽到就問:嘩 你21歲就有車拿? 咁叻仔既 <br />\n<br />\n我:其實2手車黎既 不過都算自己儲錢買落 都幾有成功感架 <br />\n<br />\n之後佢地冇乜再點攻擊我 我就禁下手機 食下飯 好快就已經到左10點幾 <br />\n<br />\n我:都夜喇 我要落樓下拎車先 廢事比d街童hi花我部車 <br />\n<br />\n點知佢姑姐話:咦 你係咪住xxx果頭啊? 不如車埋我地啊 <br />\n<br />\n我聽到已經心知不妙 我話:下..唔係幾方便喎..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢:唔係咁小氣掛 有車都唔車埋我地番去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我:但我架車剩係車到1個人炸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢:趕絕外母型? 跑車黎架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我:下 你講咩啊??? 單車黎炸喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6b4c16d8426670fd8db756febf6daed4c4983c","tid":223121,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"Thx樓上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3c94fb7c0f8a76842dade205640d6374cc8490","tid":223121,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:29:04.000Z","msg":"而家d會員都唔知你up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcdf6b35233ac845eb3ee04be4aeae230cdd23f","tid":223121,"uid":7079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:32:42.000Z","msg":"好撚有回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4726bc5548b7c6dc3aa16b9411fd6539f4e63266","tid":223121,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家d會員都唔知你up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我色囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705a74da566dcbb72bd768588fcb9d5e52a0b2fb","tid":223121,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家d會員都唔知你up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我色囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}